25:34.289 --> 25:36.708
<i>Oh, my gosh,
is my locust tree dropping pods</i>

25:36.708 --> 25:38.460
<i>onto Mr. Kim's hydrangeas again?</i>

25:38.460 --> 25:41.421
<i>No, uh, it's just a...
it's just a heads-up really.</i>

25:41.421 --> 25:43.089
<i>You know, as a friend.</i>

25:43.089 --> 25:45.300
<i>Sure.</i>

25:45.300 --> 25:47.135
<i>Yeah.</i>

25:52.265 --> 25:53.642
<i>Um...</i>

25:54.726 --> 25:57.354
<i>Did you know Adam Martin?</i>

25:58.772 --> 25:59.981
<i>Adam Martin?</i>

25:59.981 --> 26:02.400
<i>He's a...
