26:47.362 --> 26:49.656
<i>Which he definitely was.</i>

26:49.656 --> 26:51.116
<i>Mom, come on!</i>

26:51.116 --> 26:53.118
<i>Oh, Callie, hi. Um...</i>

26:53.118 --> 26:55.161
<i>this is my friend Kevyn.
