27:05.880 --> 27:07.716
<i>"Code Red," apparently.
- No, no, no, no.</i>

27:07.716 --> 27:09.676
<i>Sorry to bug you.
- No.</i>

27:09.676 --> 27:12.178
<i>Listen, we'll, uh...</i>

27:12.178 --> 27:14.931
<i>we'll be in touch if we have
any more questions, okay?</i>

27:16.808 --> 27:18.518
<i>More questions?</i>

27:18.518 --> 27:20.270
<i>Do-do I need a lawyer?</i>

27:20.270 --> 27:22.397
<i>Why would you need a lawyer?</i>

27:24.023 --> 27:26.401
<i>I don't know.
